      "message": "Patch Set 3: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nI think just replacing the locking with a commint about impossibility of the purposed race, since no other threads have a way to access this request before it was sent would be enough.\nEven though there is not going to be any contention, locked insturctions are expensive and we don't need any more cpu load on the servers, esp. on MDTs.",
